arch:property.oc:show_val: A medium-sized assemblage. Fair amount of IDs. Weathering not at all severe. Only a few digested pieces. Fair amount of manganese staining. Quite a bit of 007 sized, plus 003 sized bone. 2 equid pelves, both RHS, one more reduced around pubis area than

arch:string.div: The unique identifier for each contextual unit, matching those used in the central Çatalhöyük excavation database and in publications. The excavation uses single-context recording.
